      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are people to talk to, but it doesn't change the reality. everyone only liked the \"perfect\" version of me. now that's gone, there's nothing left for them to love. it feels like i'm just haunting my own life, pretending to be someone who isn't even there anymore. it's just exhausting to keep up the act when the real me is already gone.",
