      "content": "but that's just it... there's nothing \"real\" underneath. it's just a void. when i look in the mirror, i don't even recognize the eyes looking back. the person who could actually handle life, the one who had a future... they died when everything collapsed. i feel like i'm just a ghost waiting for my body to realize it's supposed to be gone too.",
